fullDescription.text:
Reports a 'for' loop that contains neither initialization nor an update component. Suggests replacing the loop with a simpler 'while' statement. Example: 'for(; exitCondition(); ) {
    process();
  }' After the quick-fix is applied the result looks like: 'while(exitCondition()) {
    process();
  }' Use the checkbox below if you wish this inspection to ignore for loops with trivial or non-existent conditions. Inspection ID: ForLoopReplaceableByWhileJS

